  { country_id: 12, fact_1: "The Netherlands is one of the weakest countries when it comes to the representation of women in STEM - notably science - fields.", source_1: "http://www.slate.com/blogs/better_life_lab/2017/11/09/the_stem_paradox_why_are_muslim_majority_countries_producing_so_many_female.html",
